### EK validator dimensions canon: accept windowsill depth band (2026-05-04)

**Commit `e9acfee`.** `eurocut_dimensions_canon` was hard-flagging Villu N-arm CT depth=778mm (= 600 carcass + 178mm windowsill extension) as a defect. Studiokook layout legitimately includes "столешница в подоконник" — kitchen with countertop continuing into a windowsill above the work zone. New depth band: `[600±0]` (canonical) OR `[700, 850]` (windowsill variant). Standards-rule summary updated to document the variant.

