**Wave 3 (commit `49b2589`):** built_in_dishwasher_aligned_to_neighbors, style_consistency (warning), corner_joinery_internal_parts. Snapshot extended with `:child_def_counts` for corner instances (single-level walk into `inst.definition.entities.grep ComponentInstance`). Corner BLEND regex spans library versions: legacy `BLEND*` plus EK 5.0.2 ru `PANEL_V_L / PANEL_V_R / PANEL_V_CUT_[LR] / PANEL_BLEND`. style_consistency takes def_name `_FRES/_GOLA` suffix as style; minority instances among kitchen-furniture roles get a warning.

